txt.en: A Captain is someone to look up to and admire. Their sound technique and valour inspires others to keep fighting.
Land a Critical or Devastate with Valiant Strike or Inspire
When a warrior falls in battle, it is not enough to simply ease their pain if the battle is to be won -- they must be made ready for battle again as quickly as possible.
It is said that a true sign of the Kings of old was the power to heal the sick and injured. Perhaps a trace of their blood runs through your veins?
